# CreativeFlow – Invoice Generation System

## Software Requirements Specification (SRS) & System Architecture Document

### Version 1.0

---

# 1. Project Information

## Project Name

**CreativeFlow – Invoice Generation System**

## Business Domain

Graphics Design, Flex Printing, Photography, Videography, Branding & Creative Services

## Project Type

Single Page Web Application

## Objective

To provide a simple, professional, and fast invoice generation system that allows business owners to create, print, and download invoices within one minute.

---

# 2. Problem Statement

Most graphics and printing businesses create invoices manually using:

* Excel Sheets
* MS Word
* WhatsApp Messages
* Paper Bills

Problems faced:

* Time-consuming billing process
* Calculation errors
* Unorganized customer records
* Unprofessional invoice format
* No invoice tracking

CreativeFlow solves these problems through an automated invoice generation system.

---

# 3. Project Scope

### Included in Version 1

✅ Customer Details

✅ Dynamic Service Entry

✅ Auto Invoice Number

✅ Auto Date Generation

✅ Real-Time Calculations

✅ Discount Management

✅ Advance Payment Tracking

✅ Balance Due Calculation

✅ Print Invoice

✅ Download PDF

✅ Responsive Design

---

### Not Included in Version 1

❌ Customer Database

❌ Login System

❌ Invoice History

❌ Reports Dashboard

❌ WhatsApp Integration

❌ Email Integration

❌ Expense Tracking

❌ Order Management

---

# 4. User Roles

## Business Owner

The only user of the system.

Responsibilities:

* Create invoices
* Print invoices
* Download invoices
* Calculate customer payments

---

# 5. Business Workflow

```text
Customer Arrives
       │
       ▼
Enter Customer Details
       │
       ▼
Add Services
       │
       ▼
Auto Calculate Amount
       │
       ▼
Apply Discount
       │
       ▼
Add Advance Payment
       │
       ▼
Generate Invoice
       │
       ▼
Print / Save PDF
```

---

# 6. Functional Requirements

## FR-01 Customer Information

The system shall allow the user to enter:

| Field         | Required |
| ------------- | -------- |
| Customer Name | Yes      |
| Mobile Number | Yes      |
| Address       | No       |
| Business Name | No       |

---

## FR-02 Invoice Information

The system shall automatically generate:

### Invoice Number

Format:

```text
INV-YYYYMMDD-001
```

Example:

```text
INV-20260621-001
```

### Invoice Date

Auto-filled with current date.

---

## FR-03 Service Entry

The system shall allow multiple service entries.

### Fields

| Field        |
| ------------ |
| Service Name |
| Quantity     |
| Rate         |
| Tax (%)      |
| Amount       |

---

### Supported Services

```text
Logo Design
Banner Design
Poster Design
Flex Printing
Visiting Card Design
Wedding Photography
Videography
Video Editing
Album Design
Social Media Post Design
Other
```

---

## FR-04 Calculations

### Item Amount

```javascript
Amount = Quantity × Rate
```

### Tax Amount

```javascript
Tax Amount = Amount × Tax / 100
```

### Subtotal

```javascript
Subtotal = Sum(All Item Amounts)
```

### Grand Total

```javascript
Grand Total =
Subtotal +
Tax Total -
Discount
```

### Balance Due

```javascript
Balance Due =
Grand Total -
Advance Paid
```

---

## FR-05 Summary Section

The system shall display:

```text
Subtotal

Tax Total

Discount

Grand Total

Advance Paid

Balance Due
```

---

## FR-06 Notes Section

Optional notes can be added.

Example:

```text
Thank you for choosing Pratham Creation.

Delivery within 3 days.
```

---

## FR-07 Invoice Actions

The system shall provide:

### Add Service

Add a new service row.

### Clear Form

Reset invoice data.

### Print Invoice

Print the invoice.

### Generate PDF

Download invoice as PDF.

---

# 7. Non-Functional Requirements

## Performance

* Invoice generation < 1 second
* Real-time calculations

## Usability

* Easy to use
* Minimal clicks
* Beginner-friendly interface

## Compatibility

* Chrome
* Edge
* Firefox
* Brave

## Responsive Design

* Desktop
* Laptop
* Tablet
* Mobile

---

# 8. System Architecture

## Architecture Overview

Version 1 follows a client-side architecture.

```text
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│       User Interface        │
│      HTML + CSS Layer       │
└─────────────┬───────────────┘
              │
              ▼
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│     Business Logic Layer    │
│        JavaScript           │
└─────────────┬───────────────┘
              │
              ▼
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│         Data Layer          │
│ Local Storage / JSON Object │
└─────────────────────────────┘
```

---

# 9. Layer Description

## Presentation Layer

### Technology

* HTML5
* CSS3
* Bootstrap 5

### Responsibilities

* Display invoice form
* Display totals
* Display service table
* Display buttons

---

## Business Logic Layer

### Technology

* JavaScript ES6

### Responsibilities

* Generate invoice number
* Generate date
* Calculate amounts
* Calculate taxes
* Calculate discounts
* Generate PDF
* Print invoice

---

## Data Layer

### Technology

* Browser Local Storage

### Responsibilities

* Store invoice temporarily
* Save generated invoice data
* Restore invoice if page reloads

---

