# 14. Future Upgrade Architecture (Version 2)

```text
Frontend (HTML/CSS/JS)
          │
          ▼
Flask REST API
          │
          ▼
PostgreSQL Database
          │
          ▼
Invoice Storage
Customer Records
Payment Records
```

### Additional Features

* Customer Management
* Invoice History
* Payment Tracking
* WhatsApp Sharing
* Email Integration
* Reports Dashboard

---

# 15. Expected Outcome

The Invoice Generation System should allow the business owner to:

* Create professional invoices in less than one minute.
* Automatically calculate totals and balances.
* Print invoices instantly.
* Download invoices as PDF.
* Operate without requiring a backend in Version 1.
* Serve as the foundation for a complete Graphics Business Management System in future versions.

